item.title: About
item.description: I’m a front-end engineer currently working at Garmin on Garmin Connect. I use Backbone and React to make visualizations for fitness data. I like playing basketball, I’m an avid Clemson football fan, and I’m currently working on my Master’s at Georgia Tech.
